data.title: Kiss Me Goodbye
data.meta_description: Kiss Me Goodbye - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document contains the lyrics in Japanese, romanized Japanese, and English to the song "Kiss Me Goodbye" by Angela Aki. The lyrics describe saying goodbye to a loved one and telling them to follow their dreams and not be held back, even though it means losing them. They will carry the memory of their love with them always.
